trans-unit.source: Represents the smart label properties of an annotation to store.
trans-unit.target: Representerar smart etikett egenskaperna för en anteckning för lagring.

trans-unit.source: This class is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle> class used for <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen härleds från den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle>klass som används för <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle"></xref> class with the specified chart element.

trans-unit.source: The chart element that this style belongs to.
trans-unit.target: Diagramelement som tillhör det här formatet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the back color of the label callout.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger bakgrundsfärg för etiketten bildtexter.

trans-unit.source: This property is only applicable when the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle*> property is set to a value of <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelCalloutStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen gäller endast när den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle*>egenskap är inställd på värdet <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelCalloutStyle"> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationSmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle*>

trans-unit.source: This property is for internal use and is hidden at design time and run time.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> object that represents the back color of the label callout.
